<div class="container">
    <h1 class="display-8 mt-4 mb-5">Kontakta oss</h1>
    <h2 class="display-6 mt-4">
        Dina frågor är viktiga för oss. Vänligen fyll i och skicka ditt meddelande
        via mail-formuläret nedan.</h2>
    <form class="row g-3 needs-validation" novalidate>
        <div class="col-md-4 mt-4">
            <div class="form-outline">
                <input type="text" class="form-control" placeholder="Förnamn" required />
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-4 mt-4">
            <div class="form-outline">
                <input type="text" class="form-control" placeholder="Efternamn" required />
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-4 mt-4">
            <div class="input-group form-outline">
                <input type="tel" class="form-control" placeholder="Telefonnummer" aria-describedby="inputGroupPrepend"
                    required />
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="form-group">
            <label for="comment">Meddelande:</label>
            <textarea class="form-control" rows="5" id="comment"></textarea>
        </div>
        <div class="form-check mt-4">
            <input class="form-check-input" type="checkbox" id="checkTerms" required />
            <label class="form-check-label" for="checkTerms">Jag accepterar
                <a class="text-dark"href="#">villkoren</a></label>
        </div>
        <div class="col-6 mt-4">
            <button class="btn btn-primary btn-md" type="submit">Skicka</button>
        </div>
    </form>
    <h3 class="mt-4">
        Ring eller besök oss gärna:</h3>
